OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FA waste and recycling company has been
OL,8,Ffined after an employee suffered life-
OL,9,Fchanging injuries after being crushed
OL,10,Fby a telehandler.
OL,12,FSheridan Skips Burnley Limited was
OL,13,Fhanded a #24,000 fine after their
OL,14,Femployee Jordan Campion was crushed
OL,15,Fagainst a wall by a reversing
OL,16,Ftelehandler on 12 March 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
