OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FThe 21-year-old was sorting and
OL,8,Fseparating material by hand along with
OL,9,Fthree co-workers at the Smiths Yard
OL,10,Fsite, on Clifton Street, when the
OL,11,Ftelehandler reversed into him.
OL,13,FMr Campion suffered multiple
OL,14,Ffractures, nerve damage to his right
OL,15,Farm, and internal organ injuries. He
OL,16,Falso lost partial hearing in his right
OL,17,Fear and permanent sight loss in his
OL,18,Fright eye.
OL,20,FHe was in hospital for nearly two
OL,21,Fweeks following the crash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FIn his victim personal statement, Mr
OL,8,FCampion said: "My incident has caused
OL,9,Fmy family great distress. They
OL,10,Fpermanently worry about me; they never
OL,11,Fthought that I wouldn't be safe in
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,F"They say you never expect to see your
OL,15,Fchild go off to work and to get a
OL,16,Fphone call to say that they have had
OL,17,Fan incident and might not survive."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Executives (HSE) found that
OL,9,FSheridan Skips Burnley Limited had not
OL,10,Fproperly assessed the risks that come
OL,11,Fwith having employees working
OL,12,Falongside vehicles.
OL,14,FThere was also no physical protection
OL,15,Ffrom moving vehicles, such as barriers.
OL,17,FThe investigation also found that the
OL,18,Ftelehandler was missing mirrors making
OL,19,Fit impossible for the driver to see
OL,20,Fclearly while reversing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FSheridan Skips Burnley Limited, of
OL,8,FCathedral Gates, Manchester, pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to breaching Section 2(1) of
OL,10,Fthe Health and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,11,F1974.
OL,13,FThe company was fined #24,000 and
OL,14,Fordered to pay #4,777 in costs at
OL,15,FBlackburn Magistrates' Court on 11
OL,16,FMarch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,8,FAnthony Banks said: "This young man's
OL,9,Finjuries could so easily have been
OL,10,Favoided with the implementation of
OL,11,Fsafe working practices, including
OL,12,Fpedestrian and vehicle segregation and
OL,13,Fsafe refuges for workers whilst
OL,14,Fvehicles were operating.
OL,16,F"These measures would have ensured
OL,17,Fthat workers present in the yard were
OL,18,Fnot put at risk of being struck by
OL,19,Fvehicles moving in and around where
OL,20,Fthey were working.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773421882
OL,3,CRecycling company fined after accident
OL,4,Cleaves worker with life changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,F"This should serve as a reminder to
OL,8,Fbusinesses operating in the waste
OL,9,Findustry to ensure that workplace
OL,10,Ftransport is appropriately considered,
OL,11,Fwith control measures introduced to
OL,12,Fensure the appropriate separation of
OL,13,Fvehicles and pedestrians."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
